    "\n",
    "**Your Task:**\n",
    "```python\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "# Your Uri parcel sizes (simplified)\n",
    "sizes = np.array([100, 500, 1000, 2500, 10000, 50, 750, 3000])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calculate statistics\n",
    "print(f\"Mean: {sizes.mean():.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Median: {np.median(sizes):.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Std Dev: {sizes.std():.2f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Min: {sizes.min()}, Max: {sizes.max()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Normalize to 0-1 range (min-max scaling)\n",
    "normalized = (sizes - sizes.min()) / (sizes.max() - sizes.min())\n",
    "print(f\"\\nNormalized: {normalized}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Standardize (z-score normalization)\n",
    "standardized = (sizes - sizes.mean()) / sizes.std()\n",
    "print(f\"\\nStandardized: {standardized}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Standardized mean: {standardized.mean():.10f} (should be ~0)\")\n",
    "print(f\"Standardized std: {standardized.std():.10f} (should be ~1)\")\n",
    "```\n",
